Composite lets you compose objects into tree structures
and then work with these structures as if they were individual objects.

**** Problem that it solves ****
Consider a scenario of a Corporate where each employee holds some reward points and you are asked to write a solution to get all the points for the departments
Based on these points a final rating will be drawn and departments will be ranked accordingly.

Note :- ** Reward points are provided to employee's based on impact of their work on the organization.


Component => Interface with Common Operation for leaf as well as composite
Composite => Class Holding instances of composite and providing low level operations on them
Leaf      => The smallest unit in the tree

In above scenario

Leaf => Employee
Composite => Department
Component => holds getTotalRating method

Let's get started with Code :)